Well, I always found, you know, that usually your enemies know more about you than you do yourself.

36:30.474 --> 36:31.376
Okay?

36:31.416 --> 36:32.277
They do, you know.

36:32.998 --> 36:40.450
An example, when the first contingent of Americans went over to Spain,

36:40.868 --> 36:42.270
They left New York City.

36:42.290 --> 36:45.635
It was supposed to be very hush, hush, hush.

36:45.675 --> 36:48.438
They got off the boat in Sherbird or something like that.

36:49.860 --> 36:52.384
The next day, the French newspaper had their names.

36:55.368 --> 36:57.070
The French right-wing newspaper.

36:57.090 --> 36:58.993
Well, we used to say, loose lips think shit.

36:59.013 --> 37:05.662
Well, not loose lips, but I mean, you know, the left is watching the right, and the right is watching the left.

37:06.523 --> 37:09.627
And they're gathering information on each other.

37:09.647 --> 37:10.048
So...

37:10.501 --> 37:12.903
That's the way it operates, you know.

37:13.924 --> 37:15.946
So, okay.

37:16.426 --> 37:21.551
Then you retired from this position, I guess you said, in 89, I guess, right?

