Yeah, 87, 89.

37:22.352 --> 37:24.534
87, 89.

37:24.754 --> 37:28.017
But you still maintained an office there at Brandeis, I guess.

37:28.117 --> 37:40.508
Well, what happened was that another organization called the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives, which is chartered as an educational institution, was founded.

