41:17.899 --> 41:18.981
Titles.

41:19.001 --> 41:19.161
Huh?

41:19.181 --> 41:19.561
2,000 titles.

41:19.681 --> 41:23.426
Well, titles and, you know, printings and stuff like that, some kind of it.

