How do you spell it?

41:27.651 --> 41:30.234
L-A-N-C-E-R.

41:30.255 --> 41:31.476
And when I start, you know,

41:31.895 --> 41:41.269
digging around the records there, like, who's writing what, you know, so that people there are usually seeing them, even for good stuff, you know.

41:41.289 --> 41:44.053
Well, what kind of stuff did they... Well, they published everything.

41:44.073 --> 41:45.695
