45:19.547 --> 45:20.368
But I mean...

45:21.091 --> 45:21.692
It was.

45:21.712 --> 45:23.235
That didn't interest me, the writing.

45:23.256 --> 45:25.180
The writing didn't interest me.

45:25.200 --> 45:28.587
