46:10.450 --> 46:14.253
We go around, we collect all the office papers and everything like that.

46:15.915 --> 46:17.036
That's piddling.

46:17.476 --> 46:23.262
The real meat of research is in not the office papers, but in their agent's papers.

46:25.464 --> 46:27.626
Want to expand on that?

46:27.646 --> 46:30.629
