I mean, I think there is one that I've read about.

46:59.346 --> 47:09.280
It's out in Oregon, you know, a guy who was an agent for, guys who wrote for Western Pulp Magazine, you know.

47:09.563 --> 47:12.226
So they're going to find a lot of pseudonym information.

47:12.726 --> 47:18.192
