47:33.847 --> 47:34.428
Absolutely.

47:34.568 --> 47:38.372
Should these files ever go into... So, you know, that's where, you know, that's where you've got to use...

47:38.690 --> 47:47.721
every bit of acumen, you know, to find out, you know, what is available and what you can use for research.

